ns0:DescribedValueSet.ns0:Purpose: (Clinical Focus: This value set contains concepts that represent types of environments used to identify inpatient/acute care hospital.),(Data Element Scope: This value set may use the Quality Data Model (QDM) category Encounter or attribute Admission Source. The intent of this data element is to identify environment types that define inpatient/acute care hospital. ),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes only relevant concepts associated with SNOMED CT codes that identify the environment hierarchy to define Inpatient/acute care hospital.),(Exclusion Criteria: No exclusions.)
